data.description: Great home located in West Lancaster, Home offers 4 spacious  bedrooms and 2 full baths, Formal living room and Family room with a fireplace that opens to the kitchen. Kitchen has  plenty a of counter space and Pantry. Master Bathroom offers a Safe Step Walk in Tub. Desert scape backyard with a covered patio for those hot sunny days. Home is also near schools, shopping centers, restaurants and the 14 Freeway.
